abstract: The Dow industrials slid as the dollar strengthened and commodity prices fell.
snippet: The Dow industrials slid as the dollar strengthened and commodity prices fell.
lead_paragraph: Wall Street shares slid sharply on Thursday as a stronger dollar lured investors away from riskier stock markets and commodities like gold and oil.

headline.main: Indexes Fall as Rising Dollar Lures Investors
headline.print_headline: Indexes Fall as Rising Dollar Lures Investors
